  <title translate="true">How to set the specimen for formatting of Task</title>
  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading1"><text styleclass="Heading1" translate="true">How to set the specimen for formatting of Task</text></para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-top:16px; line-height:1.00; background-color:#ffffff; tabstops:none;"><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Verdana; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#000000;" translate="true">Sometimes while creating a task, you may need that its description is written in a particular format, has some specific points, and is formatted as per the requirements. You can use templates of categories for this purpose. Template is a common HTML-document, created in the inbuilt editor in the same way as general description of the task is set.</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="line-height:1.00; background-color:#ffffff; tabstops:none;"><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Verdana; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#000000;" translate="true">So as to set the template for a particular category, go to the page of this category, and then — to the tab &quot;</text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Verdana; font-weight:bold; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#000000;" translate="true">Category Template</text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Verdana; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#000000;" translate="true">&quot;. Thereafter, when you are finished with the formatting of template in the editor, press the button</text><text styleclass="apple-converted-space" style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none; text-transform:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#000000; background-color:transparent; letter-spacing:normal; letter-scaling:100%;" translate="true">&#32;</text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Verdana; font-weight:bold; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#000000;" translate="true">&quot;Save&quot;</text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Verdana; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#000000;" translate="true">.</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-top:16px; line-height:1.00; background-color:#ffffff; tabstops:none;"><image src="categories_template_en.png" scale="100.00%" padding="1 0 1 0" styleclass="Image Caption"></image></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-top:16px; line-height:1.00; background-color:#ffffff; tabstops:none;"><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Verdana; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#000000;" translate="true">Description of the task when created will look like:</text></para>
